{"tid":1031762,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"終於開竅：香港唔係冇 IT，係「好多」IT🙂","createTime":"2019-02-22T01:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T03:37:38.000Z","uid":125976,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53d34efa45d6968e6174c3b9093a6b6ce444ffb5","tid":1031762,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"金融佬可以呃盡 funding 喺香港開 Software House<br />\n<br />\n新聞佬可以喺香港開 Software House (eg. HK01)<br />\n<br />\n印刷佬可以喺香港開 Software House (eg. e-print)<br />\n<br />\n連街邊賣魚蛋嗰個都可以喺香港開 IT Firm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯獨真正 IT 狗喺香港撈 IT 就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIT 喺香港係錢同人脈嘅遊戲<br />\n<br />\n食到𠵱條水嘅都係富後代嘅外行人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以你喺其他行頭做到咁上吓成績，都可以開 IT Firm，食盡創科熱潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為最後都係班 IT 狗收皮，但你始終有賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462239a8d519c06c56294f8e6b727d7fc609a2b1","tid":1031762,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"食左藥未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28447f46f0fe930b61c03102fb23df55e35af824","tid":1031762,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"462239a8d519c06c56294f8e6b727d7fc609a2b1","tid":1031762,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"食左藥未<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-22T01:19:31.000Z","msg":"想我請你食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2266c1461bb86e884d7cd47f9cc97d122a583c59","tid":1031762,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28447f46f0fe930b61c03102fb23df55e35af824","tid":1031762,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid